         <abstract>
            <p>We study the best approximation of a divergence-free function by a divergence-free algebraic or trigonometric polynomial and we prove an optimal estimate. In a particular case we give also an optimal result for the polynomial approximation of a function and its divergence.</p>
          </abstract>
